::Prowl::

Prowl walks behind Iron Raptor, deep in thought. He was beggining to 
see something developing here.. Prowl walks back over to Epyon.

"I might not be an architect, but I'm a military strategist. I think I 
could make a good design to successfully defend against enemy 
attacks."

He looks up at the Cybertronian Fire. The technology in the Neo Beast 
Wars had obvioustly expanded beyond the point where normal bases were 
no longer efficient. It was time to move on.
